summary: This mod add Cute Elves Race to the game
descriptionHtml:
[color=pink][size=6]DESCRIPTION[/size][/color]
This mod add Cute Elves Race to the game.
History of  race:
Once Spriggans sheltered children elves. Spriggans been kind to him, taught them magic, applied it to children to make them stronger. At one point, the children - that is already grown elves discovered that  they are not like the others and possess magic and beautiful appearance, so the race of Cute Elves.

Skills:
2H weapon = 5
Alchemy =5
ELoquence - 5 
1H weapon = 10
Destruction = 5

Magic:
Cute Elf Magic - Spriggan like magic
Cute Elf Resistance - Resistance to Shock,Fire,Frost
Cute Elf Heal - Healing once a day
Cute Elf Paralyze 

[color=pink][size=6]SETUP[/size][/color]
Put all files to Data folder

[color=pink][size=6]UNINSTALL[/size][/color]
Delete
meshes/CuteElf
textures/CuteElf

Thanks you for your help [/size]
